quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  72,1,"Yeele: ""b kõo maam kɩbare, tɩ yel sẽn yalẽ, zĩn-dãmb zãma n wɑ n kelg mɑm kɑrengã, n lebg n tɩ yeel-b nebã: ""ad tõnd wʋma kaoreng (Alkʋrãaa) sẽn yaa yel-soalma""."
  72,2,"A peegd n tʋgdɑ kãndgrẽ, tɩ tõnd kõ sɩd ne-a, la tõnd kõn tol n lagem ne d Soabã ned ba a yembre ye."
  72,3,"Tõnd Soabã zɩslmã sekame, a pa tar paga; pa biig me."
  72,4,"Ad tõnd yalmã (a Ibliis) rag n yetda Wẽnd zug gomd sẽn zʋʋg toadga."
  72,5,"La tõnd tẽeme tɩ ninsaalbã la zĩn-dãmbã kon tol n yeel Wẽnd zug pʋ-yagb ye."
  72,6,"Yel sẽn yalẽ yεsã, roap n da be n yaa ninsaalbɑ, n baood gũudum ne roap sẽn ya zĩn-dãmbɑ, tɩ b paas-b raagre."
  72,7,"La bãmb tẽeme wala yãmb sẽn tẽ wã, tɩ Wẽnd pa na n tol n yik ned ba a yembr ye."
  72,8,"Lɑ tõnd sɩɩsa saagã n mik tɩ b pids-a lame ne gũudb sẽn tar pãng la bug-vɩlense."
  72,9,"La tõnd ra yɩɩme n zĩ a pʋgẽ zĩndg zĩisẽ n nɑ kelg Mɑlek-rãmbã sẽn tɑɑsd tɑɑbã, la ned ning sẽn bɑo ɑ kelgr moasã, a paamda bug-vɩlenga."
  72,10,"La tõnd pa mi yaa wẽng la b rat ne sẽn be b tẽngã zugu, bɩ b Soabã rat-b-la ne kãndgr ye."
  72,11,"La be tõnd pʋgẽ, sẽn yaa nin-sõmse, be tõnd pʋgẽ me sẽn pa rẽnda, tõnd yɩɩme n yaa sula n yaa toor-toore."
  72,12,"La ad tõnd tẽeme tɩ tõnd kõn tol n põsg Wẽnd Tẽngã zugu, d le kõn tol n põsg-A ne zoees ye."
  72,13,"La tõndo, wakat ning d sẽn wʋm kãndgrã, d kõo sɩd ne-A, la ned ning sẽn kõt sɩd ne a Soabã, bɩ a ra yaees bõne, a ra yaees mongre!"
  72,14,"La sɑk-n-tũ-rãmbɑ (moeembɑ) bee tõnd pʋgẽ, la kɩfr-rãmb me bee tõnd pʋgẽ, neb nins sẽn tũud-bã, bãmb rãmb n togl kãndgre."
  72,15,"La sã n yaa wẽgdbã, bãmb yɩɩme n yaa Gεhannem rɑɑdo"
  72,16,"Bãmb sã n da tẽegẽ-la tɩrga, D na yũnugẽ-b koom sẽn waooge."
  72,17,"Sẽn na yɩlẽ n bugs-b a pʋgẽ. Ned ning sẽn wa n ball n yi a Soabã tẽegre, A kẽesd-a-la naong rʋʋgdgẽ."
  72,18,"La ad misa wã yaa Wẽnd n so, bɩ y ra kos n lagem Wẽnd ne ned ba a yembr ye."
  72,19,"La ad Wẽnd yambã (Mohammad) sẽn wa n yãsẽ n tũud-A wã, bilf tɩ b (zĩn-dãmbã) lebg wala zerd a zugu, (b sẽn sũ keelem n kelgd ɑ Kɑrengã)."
  72,20,"Yeele: ""ad mam kota m Soabã, la m pa lagem ne-A ned ba a yembre ye""."
  72,21,"Yeele: ""mam pa tar sẽn namsd yãmba, m leb n pa so yãmb kãndgr ye""."
  72,22,"Yeele: ""ad maam, ned ba a yembr pa tõe n põsg maam n yi Wend ye, m leb n kõn paam lallg zĩig sã n pa Yẽnd nengẽ ye."
  72,23,"Ralla taasg sẽn yi Wẽnd nengẽ la A Tẽn-tʋmdã; la ned ning sẽn kɩɩsd-a Wẽnd la A Tẽn-tʋʋmã, ad Gεhanm Bugum n be ne-a, b yaa duumdb a pʋgẽ lae-lae."
  72,24,"Hal tɩ b sã n wa yã bũmb ning b sẽn pʋlem bãmbã, b na n bãngame ned ning sõngd sẽn valemse, la a sõor sẽn paoode."
  72,25,"Yeele: ""m pa mi b sẽn pʋlem yãmb bũmb ningã pẽeme bɩ mam Soabã na n maan-a lame t'a zãr ye?"
  72,26,"Yẽ lɑ sẽn solg Mita, A pa vẽnegd A solgrã n wilg ned ba a yembr ye."
  72,27,"Ralla ned ning A sẽn yard-a soab sẽn yaa Tẽn-tʋʋma, rẽnd A kẽesdɑ gũudb yẽ neng taoore la a poor wεεngẽ, (pʋlyĩng tɩ bõn-zẽng rɑ wʋm ye)."
  72,28,"Bʋl yĩng t'a (tẽn-tʋʋmã)bãnge, tɩ tẽn-tʋʋbã sẽn deng yẽ wã sɩd taasa b Soabã tẽn-tʋmdã. A leb n gũbga ne bũmb ning sẽn be bãmb nengẽ wã, A leb n tigma bãmb fãa gill ne sõore."
